{"tid":1312442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以下係我係公立醫院病房聽到既野","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T17:13:26.000Z","uid":112700,"like":736,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"96c1107d2e617264aabd6fe1605762ac7670d00a","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"聽到APN比成班RN既指引，淨係聽到幾句。<br />\n<br />\n1:<br />\n醫護人員問起傷口時，病人有權拒絕透露傷口形成的原因。除非病人承認傷口來自槍械/布袋彈，醫護人員才需要上報，否則亦毋須深究。<br />\n<br />\n2:<br />\n病人入院時可要求院方拒絕批露任何病人私隱，會有相應措施提供，小至拒絕作答某病人是否住院/鎖起牌板etc<br />\n<br />\n3:<br />\n當有警察來到病房，要與某病人「傾下謁」，院方不會要求醫護人員拒權警察進入病房，惟醫護人員必須檢查委任證。<br />\n<br />\n好過分囉，垃圾HA包庇暴徒<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隱瞞傷口來源</span></span></strong>，處處維護暴徒，比佢地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向院方要求隱瞞病人資訊</span></span></strong>，可恥！"},{"pid":"a7da684b7f09d9d4ecf870e961924fa1813778a1","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":3,"dislike":29,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"3f635e2c55432a8a2d26f0a4a524d4e23d106f85","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:47:04.000Z","msg":"推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"6370b0225f74d33fdb67a9ec92ea849beaa90e81","tid":1312442,"uid":54181,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7884272ee6288f15c1814e5689550bc8609f7399","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"1cbc41f914b0749c1f95cbddbdfdf714d665a8d4","tid":1312442,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"695ca65bf009d9b66b154ce1045f56ad6d9294c4","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"「你個傷口成個窿咁既，點黎架？」<br />\n<span style=\"font