"請求大家幫手推po，一定要比更多人睇到。"},{"pid":"a1125bd8c3e7ae53dd1fd9ebf99084c3e0d7a303","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ba78ab36e0cc772d1bee446a1e8031981c1104","tid":1312442,"uid":31975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"八唔八到QE A&amp;E 條八婆有無比人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"請上fb search ha secret"},{"pid":"2f86038e6ec336cc15664428532e3fd3ece7ba1f","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"繼續推比大家睇下HA有幾可恥"},{"pid":"157f3cbfb4bc2e0e951fb975411e6e01ed9df151","tid":1312442,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c1107d2e617264aabd6fe1605762ac7670d00a","tid":1312442,"uid":112700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"聽到APN比成班RN既指引，淨係聽到幾句。<br />\n<br />\n1:<br />\n醫護人員問起傷口時，病人有權拒絕透露傷口形成的原因。除非病人承認傷口來自槍械/布袋彈，醫護人員才需要上報，否則亦毋須深究。<br />\n<br />\n2:<br />\n病人入院時可要求院方拒絕批露任何病人私隱，會有相應措施提供，小至拒絕作答某病人是否住院/鎖起牌板etc<br />\n<br />\n3:<br />\n當有警察來到病房，要與某病人「傾下謁」，院方不會要求醫護人員拒權警察進入病房，惟醫護人員必須檢查委任證。<br />\n<br />\n好過分囉，垃圾HA包庇暴徒<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隱瞞傷口來源</span></span></strong>，處處維護暴徒，比佢地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向院方要求隱瞞病人資訊</span></span></strong>，可恥！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"召喚陳沛然，李國麟"},{"pid":"50f94fb181436e06590b384e5cd22b53e84bf0a7","tid":1312442,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"[學術分享]今日教大家點樣整套索捉畜生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19c53a78a06063692d78841579f16267cad5d9eb","tid":1312442,"uid":269864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco